name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Mintedz - Extension for NFTs on OpenSea

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Boost your OpenSea. Save time and money.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This free Chrome Extension adds data directly on NFT collection page to OpenSea:

- NFT collection score
- NFT flipping score
- Twitter followers and Discord members
- Switch prices to US dollar
- Likes / Dislikes
- Views
- 24h volume
- 24h sales
- Creation date
- Reports number
- Ratio by owner
- Royalties
- ... and more to come!
